description: This file defines the AuthService class which provides authentication functionalities such as login, Google Sign-In, and logout using an API client and Google Sign-In package.

classes.name: AuthService
classes.description: A service class providing methods for user authentication, including login with email/password, Google Sign-In, and logout.

methods.name: login
methods.description: Performs user login with email and password, retrieves tokens and user info from API.

methods.name: googleSignIn
methods.description: Handles Google Sign-In authentication, exchanges Google ID token with backend API for tokens and user info.

methods.name: logout
methods.description: Clears stored authentication tokens, effectively logging out the user.
